summary: Netflix has The Last Jedi and I keep seeing it and going “I should put that on in the background while I putter,” and then I...
body:
Netflix has The Last Jedi and I keep seeing it and going “I should put that on in the background while I putter,” and then I scroll to it and the big preview image is where they’re back to back ready to fight and my stomach does this dramatic swoop, and I’m like, “No, no, this is way too intense for me right now. I am not prepared for this kind of emotional investment.”

You guys. That picture is so affecting, it literally intimidates me into not watching the movie.

Wtf.
